🖥️ How It Works
Captures real-time hand gestures using OpenCV.
Processes images through a trained deep learning model.
Classifies gestures and translates them into text.
Displays recognized signs on the screen for easy interpretation.
📌 Future Enhancements
🔹 Expand sign language support (ASL, BSL, etc.)
🔹 Enhance accuracy with transformers & self-supervised learning
🔹 Sign-to-speech conversion for better accessibility
🔹 Mobile-friendly version for on-the-go use

